trans-unit.source: Represents an element in a <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElementCollection" /> class.
The <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElementCollection> class represents the \<schemeSettings> element under the Uri section within a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElementCollection>类表示\<schemeSettings > 配置文件中的 Uri 部分下的元素。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement> class represents an instance of an element in the <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElementCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement>类表示一个实例中的某个元素<xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElementCollection>类。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElementCollection> class and the \<schemeSettings> section in a configuration file looks generic, implying that an application can specify any <xref:System.GenericUriParserOptions?displayProperty=nameWithType> enumeration value for any scheme.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElementCollection>类和\<schemeSettings > 配置文件中的部分外观泛型，表示应用程序可以指定任何<xref:System.GenericUriParserOptions?displayProperty=nameWithType>任何一种方案的枚举值。

trans-unit.source: In fact, only the <xref:System.GenericUriParserOptions.DontUnescapePathDotsAndSlashes?displayProperty=nameWithType> flag for HTTP and HTTPS schemes are supported.
trans-unit.target: 在事实中，仅<xref:System.GenericUriParserOptions.DontUnescapePathDotsAndSlashes?displayProperty=nameWithType>标志的 HTTP 和 HTTPS 方案受支持。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: Gets the value of the GenericUriParserOptions entry from a <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 获取 <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement" /> 实例中 GenericUriParserOptions 项的值。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement.GenericUriParserOptions%2A> property returns a <xref:System.GenericUriParserOptions?displayProperty=nameWithType> enumeration value for the <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement> instance.
Gets the value of the Name entry from a <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 获取 <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement" /> 实例中 Name 项的值。

trans-unit.source: The protocol used by this schema setting.
trans-unit.target: 此架构设置使用的协议。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement.GenericUriParserOptions%2A> property returns a <xref:System.GenericUriParserOptions?displayProperty=nameWithType> enumeration value for the <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement> instance.
The <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement.GenericUriParserOptions%2A> element is currently restricted to HTPP and HTTPS.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement.GenericUriParserOptions%2A>元素是当前只限于 HTPP 和 HTTPS。
